{"tid":1778804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國戰線打法","createTime":"2019-12-11T08:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T14:11:32.000Z","uid":177168,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"27bb193fa8e04976c83427d14c0c95bddf6c88ed","tid":1778804,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"當年1984 簽Joint-Declaration時候，其實只不過是宗主國英國同 PRC之間的一場協議，全程港人跟本就冇話語權。<br />\n<br />\n但實際上，聯合國1960年訂立《給予殖民地國家和人民獨立宣言》，提到︰根據聯合國憲章所尊崇之各民族享有平等權利及自決權之原則，各民族一律有權自由決定其政治地位，不受外界之干涉，並追求其經濟、社會及文化之發展，且每一國均有義務遵照憲章規定尊重此種權利。 <br />\n<br />\n即使在1972年PRC取代ROC在UN入面席位，在翌年Res. 2908 將港澳剔出殖民地名單，逼使英國同PRC談判。我地的自決權依然存在。<br />\n見<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2016/11/self-determination-3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2016%2F11%2Fself-determination-3%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=d7a9fc49\" target=\"_blank\">www.localpresshk.com/2016/11/self-determination-3/</a><br />\n<br />\n要打呢條線，就要同全世界講當年英國同PRC deal 是 同 德蘇互不侵犯條約 冇分別，中國是非法霸佔香港土地。港人將行使自決原則"},{"pid":"48a6cf3c203f797ff1afb058f9d2a3cf37a56a87","tid":1778804,"uid":225934,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n今晚有英領集會<br />\n8pm"},{"pid":"339671be62e670c4458ee9674ec17c51b379eaf0","tid":1778804,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"5c4515e4eeee956341363011432bcd6a7eb02e8b","tid":1778804,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bPxdjm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbPxdjm2.jpg&h=5fcd7cd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ec542180db814888b0f5f9ab48f1c96d7567e44","tid":1778804,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac